data.description: Located in the heart of East Boca, this 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 car garage townhouse with it's open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, just recently installed porcelain tile and luxury vinyl floors, will charm you as soon as you arrive!  Roof 2020, AC 2018, HW 2019 (gas). The community amenities include a beautiful pool area, hot tub and sauna.Welcome to the beautiful Lands End, pet friendly community, with it's luscious  tropical landscape and greenery! Just minutes away from FAU, Mizner Park, the beach, Town Center Mall and Boca Hospital. Situated east of I-95 and Glades Road, allowing easy access to major highways.
